BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 6 (KCNA) -- Kang Song-san, premier 
of the Administration Council, sent a message of greetings to 
Abdel Latif Filali on his appointment as prime minister of the 
Kingdom of Morocco. 
  Believing that the friendly and cooperative relations 
between 
the two countries will grow stronger and develop in the 
interests of the two peoples, the message wishes him success in 
his work. 

</TEXT>

