<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 7 (KCNA) -- The Japanese police 
committed another fascist brutality through a wholesale 
crackdown on the Kyoto Prefectural headquarters of the General 
Association of Korean Residents in Japan (Chongnyon) in broad 
