BFN 

<F P=106> ["They Must Not Miscalculate" -- KCNA headline] </F>
  [Text] Pyongyang, June 9 (KCNA) -- NODONG SINMUN today 
comments on the U.S. act in driving the situation on the Korean 
peninsula to the phase of war. 
  Warning that it must stop its harebrained act, facing 
squarely the reality, the analyst says: 
  The United States is planning to additionally deploy a task 
force comprising a carrier flotilla, tactical flying corps, "B 
52" strategic bombers, etc. In South Korea, Japan and the west 
Pacific region. The U.S. Defense Secretary Perry said "a 
preemptive strike at Pyongyang's nuclear facilities remains an 
